@jamesob

> What's your platform information? I just tried to reproduce your error locally and was unable, and CI is able to build. Maybe try `make distclean; ./configure ...`, then remake?

I've tried all sorts of clean and make to no avail. My system is Arch and I'm using GCC 11.1. Here's the [config.log](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/files/7157670/config.log) if that's useful.

